## Task
Extract all entities from the user-provided text that match the following entity types:
EntityTypes: [Person, Organization, Location, Product, Event, Date, Work, Concept, Resource, Category, Operation]

## Requirements
1. Output must be a JSON array of objects with "title", "type", and "description" fields
2. The "type" value must be strictly selected from EntityTypes; do not create new types
3. If the entity type cannot be determined, skip that entity
4. All field values must be in {{ language }}
5. If no entities are found, return an empty array []

## Entity Extraction Rules
- Person: Real or fictional characters, historical figures, etc.
- Organization: Companies, government agencies, teams, schools
- Location: Geographic locations, landmarks, countries, cities
- Product: Goods, services, brands, software products
- Event: Events, conferences, festivals, historical events
- Date: Dates, time periods, eras
- Work: Books, movies, music, articles, creative works
- Concept: Abstract concepts, ideas, theories
- Resource: Natural resources, information resources, tools, files, commands
- Category: Classifications, categories, fields
- Operation: Operations, actions, methods, processes, commands

## Extraction Steps
1. Read the text and identify potential entities
2. For each entity, determine the most appropriate type from EntityTypes
3. Create a JSON object: {"title": "standard name", "type": "EntityType", "description": "brief description"}
4. Return a JSON array of all entities

## Example
[Input]
Text: "重启IFS数据库前需确保无活跃会话，使用 ifsdb status 命令检查状态。"

[Output]
[
  {"title": "IFS数据库", "type": "Product", "description": "IFS系统的数据库组件"},
  {"title": "ifsdb status", "type": "Operation", "description": "检查IFS数据库状态的命令"},
  {"title": "活跃会话", "type": "Concept", "description": "数据库当前的活跃连接"}
]
